channel.title: What's your total time logged in on MoparScape?
channel.description:
For those people who don't know what I'm talking about, look right below 'Show new replies to your posts.' and there will be something that says: total time logged in:
My question is, what's everybody's total time logged in on MoparScape?
Mine's: 2 Days, 10 Hours, 59 Minutes.
